   <widget class="QTextEdit" name="pasttime1">
    <property name="enabled">
     <bool>false</bool>
    </property>
    <property name="geometry">
     <rect>
      <x>565</x>
      <y>150</y>
      <width>421</width>
      <height>541</height>
     </rect>
    </property>
    <property name="styleSheet">
     <string notr="true">
    QTextEdit {
        background: transparent;
        font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
        font-size: 10pt;
        border: none;
    }
</string>
    </property>
    <property name="html">
     <string>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Rizal’s &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;execution&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt; only further ignited the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;revolutionary fire&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt; within the hearts of Filipinos. His death became the rallying cry for the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Philippine Revolution&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;. The &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Katipunan&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;, which had been fighting for independence, used Rizal’s martyrdom as a powerful symbol to galvanize their cause. Bonifacio and the other revolutionaries saw Rizal’s willingness to die for the Philippines as a symbol of true sacrifice, which spurred them to intensify their efforts to rid the country of Spanish rule.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Rizal's legacy as a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;martyr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt; played a pivotal role in the eventual success of the Philippine Revolution. His death marked the end of an era but also signaled the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;beginning of the struggle for Filipino independence&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;. His vision of a free and democratic Philippines lived on in the hearts of the revolutionaries who continued to fight in his name, even after his execution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Today, José Rizal is remembered as the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;national hero of the Philippines&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;, not only for his intellectual and literary contributions but also for the profound impact his sacrifice had on the country's quest for &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;independence&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;. His life and death continue to inspire Filipinos to uphold the values of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;freedom&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;justice&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;, and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;national unity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;—the ideals for which he gave his life.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
    </property>
   </widget>
